Class VendorConsent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iab.gdpr.VendorConsent

  • public class VendorConsent
extends Object
    This class implements a builder and a factory method for the IAB consent as specified in https://github.com/InteractiveAdvertisingBureau/GDPR-Transparency-and-Consent-Framework/blob/master/ Draft_for_Public_Comment_Transparency%20%26%20Consent%20Framework%20-%20cookie%20and%20vendor%20list%20format% 20specification%20v1.0a.pdf
